Introduction

Gaho is a South Korean singer-songwriter, producer, and member of the band KAVE. Known for his versatile musical talents, he is also a former member of the project boy group PLT. Gaho made his solo debut on May 3, 2018, with the digital single Stay Here, which showcased his ability to craft emotive and engaging music. As a member of KAVE, Gaho contributes his powerful vocals and creative input to the group’s dynamic sound. His songwriting and production skills are key to the band’s evolving music.
